      "amount": "3"
    }
  ],
  "method": [
    "Cook the pasta in a pot of salted boiling water for 10 minutes. Drain and let cool.",
    "Combine the mayonnaise, sour cream, chicken, walnuts, raisins, curry powder, salt, pepper, and scallions in a bowl.",
